----------------------------------------------------------------
NEWS file for the mmcm package
----------------------------------------------------------------

----------------------------------------------------------------

Changes in version 1.2-4 (2013-01-20)

 o Replace .First.lib() to a useDynLib directive in the
   NAMESPACE

----------------------------------------------------------------

Changes in version 1.2-3 (2012-09-03)

 o Deleted exit() functions and added error() functions in
   "mmcm.resamp.c"


----------------------------------------------------------------

Changes in version 1.2-2 (2011-09-13)

 o Revised R files for roxygen tags
 o Updated reference articles


----------------------------------------------------------------

Changes in version 1.2-1 (2011-05-16)

 o Fixed bugs for a multi-core CPUs related issue
 o Revised help files


----------------------------------------------------------------

Changes in version 1.2-0 (2011-05-16)

 o Implemented OpenMP parallelization for "mmcm.resamp" function
 o Supported one and two-sided tests


----------------------------------------------------------------

Changes in version 1.1-1 (2009-12-22)

 o Fixed a bug: inccorect contrast vector was outputed in
   "print.mmcm.res" function
 o Added absolute error tolerance option in "mmcm.resamp"
   function


----------------------------------------------------------------

Changes in version 1.1-0 (2009-12-22)

 o Added "mcm.mvt", "mmcm.mvt" function
 o Implemented the maximum contrast method


----------------------------------------------------------------

Changes in version 1.0-1 (2009-06-12)

 o Fixed a bug of a 64-bit OS related issue


----------------------------------------------------------------

Changes in version 1.0-0 (2009-01-22)

 o Released.

